{
  "stem": "11916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a big glass ceilings, big lights and everything, and it did good damage on this factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It could never be used again, this where that fell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it also damaged many of the other houses which look like houses, normal family houses, and they was all factories.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it seems to be, whoever did the bombing knew what was they doing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The prisoners, we cannot go back to our own barrack, because it was bombed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we run away, because we was told, go down in the basement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By this time, nobody care, at least not the Jews, because we was also hoping that's the end of the war, maybe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was almost, some places.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we run on the street, as many as we could, looking for our friend who might stop and can't work, because some got shock over the bomb, when we tried to hold as many as we could and run on the street.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We was catched after this, because we have no place to go, and some were-- no food, nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we was also taken to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What was it like there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have no more beds there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We go back to the floor, and as many in one room, maybe, as many could.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We do get some food, and it wasn't long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The bombing really never stop in Reichenbach.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was keep on going and going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was the time they transferred us to another factory, called Porta, about two weeks later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Another radio factory, which was also bombed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After we worked there only one week, this factory was also bombed and flooded.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After this, we was taken from there, because I think-- I don't know why, but maybe the Russian came, or whoever.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
